name: Fool's Gold
description: The Dosi never had a magical solution for the temporal anomaly crisis... but their former captives report that they may be hoarding something that could help. Will you take it by force, or hold out for one last deal?
rules:
-- Unique Dominion Faction Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Jake Sisko, B. Sisko, McCoy, Survivalists or Tribble Quark will provide a bonus to Event Faction Missions.
-- Every Event Faction Mission you succeed at earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Victory Points to unlock Event Threshold Rewards.
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Jake Sisko, B. Sisko, McCoy, Survivalists or Tribble Quark
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Missions!

featured_crew.name: Jake
featured_crew.flavor: “Jake struggles to keep up with his father’s erratic search while tending to his exhausted grandfather.”

featured_crew.name: McCoy
featured_crew.flavor: Donning an environmental suit and boarding the U.S.S. Defiant with his crewmates, McCoy seeks to find out what happened to its ill-fated crew.
